<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Contraseña Actualizada | NutriPet Vet</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #eefcff; color: #001f24; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif; }
    a { color: #005d90; text-decoration: none; }
    .email-shell { width: 100%; min-height: 100%; padding: 24px 12px; background: #eefcff; }
    .email-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .email-card { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #c3e9f1; border-radius: 28px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 22px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08); }
    .brand-bar { background: #005d90; padding: 24px 24px; text-align: center; color: #ffffff; }
    .brand-link { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: #ffffff; }
    .brand-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 9999px; background: #0077b6; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
    .brand-icon img { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; }
    .brand-title { margin: 0; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; }
    .brand-copy { margin: 12px auto 0; max-width: 420px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; }
    .email-panel { padding: 32px 28px 36px; }
    .body-copy { margin: 0 0 24px; color: #2d4351; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; }
    .note-copy { margin: 0; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; text-align: center; }
    .email-footer { background: #f0f7fc; padding: 18px 24px 24px; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.9rem; text-align: center; }
    .footer-links { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; gap: 12px; margin-top: 12px; }
    .footer-links a { text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; font-size: 0.82rem; color: #005d90; }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="email-shell">
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="email-card">
      <div class="brand-bar">
        <a href="<%= root_url %>" class="brand-link">
          <span class="brand-icon"><img src="https://i.imgur.com/1Q9Z1Zm.png" alt="NutriPet" /></span>
          NutriPet Vet
        </a>
        <p class="brand-copy">Tu plataforma clínica sigue protegida y lista para diagnosticar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-panel">
        <h1 class="brand-title">Contraseña Actualizada</h1>
        <p class="body-copy">Hola <strong><%= @resource.email %></strong>, tu contraseña se ha cambiado con éxito. Si no fuiste tú, ponte en contacto con soporte cuanto antes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <div>© 2026 NutriPet Vet</div>
        <div class="footer-links">
          <a href="<%= pages_terms_url %>">Términos</a>
          <a href="<%= pages_privacy_url %>">Privacidad</a>
          <a href="mailto:delirable@gmail.com">Contacto</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
